import React, { createRef, useState, useEffect } from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import axios from 'axios' import { Segment, Grid, Table, Menu, Label, Header, Image, Button, Icon, Divider, Confirm, Modal, Form, Input } from 'semantic-ui-react' import { element } from 'prop-types' const LandlordProfile = () => { const contextRef = createRef() const [multipleFiles, setMultipleFiles] = useState([]); const [open, setisOpen] = useState(false) const [openModal, setOpen] = useState(false) const showConfirm = () => { setisOpen(true) } const hideConfirm = () => { setisOpen(false) } const getMultipleFiles = async () => { try { const { data } = await axios.get('http://localhost:5000/api/getMultipleFiles'); return data; } catch (error) { throw error; } } const getMultipleFilesList = async () => { try { const fileslist = await getMultipleFiles(); setMultipleFiles(fileslist); } catch (error) { console.log(error); } } useEffect(() => { getMultipleFilesList() // eslint-disable-next-line react-hooks/exhaustive-deps }, []); return (
